{"type": "article", "id": 48871, "title": "这款极简衣帽钩，既可悬吊又可壁挂｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-03T23:31:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 46763, "name": "TIEL"}, {"id": 43582, "name": "ferm LIVING"}, {"id": 46764, "name": "Satël"}, {"id": 46765, "name": "Aectual"}, {"id": 46766, "name": "Pierre + Charlotte"}, {"id": 46767, "name": "Dirk Strothmann"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 120, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180103212542xpIJvBgL7Vr3XA1d.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>3D Printing Floors by Aectual </h3><p>荷兰公司 Aectual 开发出了 3D 打印地板的新技术，可以为水磨石地板添入层出不穷的颜色和图案，形状和尺寸皆可定制。Aectual 首席执行官 Hans Vermeulen 表示：“我们可以为例如酒店大堂的地板或零售品牌创建属于自己的醒目设计。”去年他们就曾为东京一家百货公司定制设计了 3D 打印地板，今年又为阿姆斯特丹一个重修的机场设计了定制地板。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212631iQ3zdPuwyZLJXj8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032126375zUFsNfKrAO4Jcui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212639CM1r0NL64cbhwvRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212641dsgiGaeo6bhHUp7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212641EDmXKHlbinQoy6AT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.359137\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Harry Trestles by Satël </h3><p>法国工作室 Satël 创造了一个极简支架，由三毫米的钢板切割弯曲制成，三条腿和顶部的八个褶皱为支架提供了稳定性和支撑力。因为制造工艺简单，用料节省，Harry 支架的生产成本很低。它可以作为桌腿使用，且可以适应不同的温度和环境，室内外环境都可以。因其巧妙轻便的形状，Harry 支架也很易于移动和存放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212725vArEU0VomRuDCp2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212726VqfwzWgpUyExmF1L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212726RbPYWuk9ZxEF8BvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212727MTDtU28FfRlK7Odu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212728AGD0Y7lgsam28bx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.257946\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212729mxylKti49QBvPAj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Magnic Microlights by Dirk Strothmann</h3><p>众筹网站 Kickstarter 最近上线了一个项目 Magnic Microlights，声称是“世界上最小的接触式无摩擦自行车发电机设施”，这是为夜骑爱好者研发的一种非接触式照明设备，利用磁铁的磁吸力，吸附到自行车铁质的刹车夹片上面。这款车灯不会产生任何摩擦，也不需要电池或电缆，它能提供无尽的能量，照亮前后轮。</p><p>此外，骑车人还可以根据需要调节灯的安装位置，可以照亮车轮或者照亮前方道路。众筹价 19 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dynamodirk/magnic-microlights-non-contact-driven-brake-shoe-b\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032129309EGygtnBAKZq6mDk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551345\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212929HR14shJWwUdyu37t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.537897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032129322KyVsY3v1o6fUpub.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032129329B7kqAS1flpYstOP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103212932UoAgI0mtH3ilxNVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Bucket Series by Pierre + Charlotte</h3><p>设计二人组 Pierre + Charlotte 先后落脚在巴黎和墨尔本，最近又搬去了塔斯马尼亚，也为他们的设计带来了全新灵感。最新推出的 Bucket 系列包括壁灯、吊灯和台灯，全部采用塔斯马尼亚当地木材制成。水桶造型的灯饰采用原木色调，灯饰的其他部分组件则由松木或是美国胡桃木制成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213012ul3V9fbFnQ0LMIhP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.906250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213012e4pqjva78H0cxhnE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213012GfmN9tTMk7EjgOph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213012sOrRgtMnC4I6fLzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213013uztmiOdKrMUCX01I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.035937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032130138HYx4tmkGTVcWJSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bubble Glass Range by ferm LIVING</h3><p>丹麦家居品牌 ferm LIVING 推出的这一系列玻璃花瓶，有一种很微妙、俏皮的性格。泡沫元素就像被冻结的时间一样，而外部的透明玻璃作为一个渠道，捕捉那些微妙的时间。圆形、矩形、拱形和阶梯形集合在一起，也算是个有趣的组合。一向擅于运用色彩的 ferm LIVING，这次完全将色彩概念放置一边，用透明的玻璃塑造的花瓶，加上其中“泡沫”的点缀，更显精致。售价 39 至 54 美元不等，<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/search.aspx?q=Bubble+Glass\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213050WyAjtgsECJqb05QZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801032130504S7MxG8yE20W6svJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213050bOHp7YNEfzo9P2ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213050MNIHGcD1aXUrh846.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213050zVmuotWKUZ8dfy2b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018010321305284KtZXpfiOLbUMRQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oblik Hanger by <a href=\"https://tiel.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TIEL</a></h3><p>对于如何在简单中创造趣味，首尔多学科创意实践工作室 TIEL 颇有心得。比如这款名为 Oblik 的衣架，设计师希望改进其形式和功能，它由坚实的橡木碎片制成，衣架被削减出不同的角度和缺口，用来挂置衣物。Oblik 有两种不同的版本：壁挂式和悬吊式。</p><p>在设计师看来，Oblik 衣架适用于那些极简主义风格的空间，需要并不抢戏且具有设计感的功能物件，Oblik 显然是个不错的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213127RktaYzuxBSKb7hEZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213127nYoixUPF3a9lBQCE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213129JtH2V7Nuzw0Q5ihZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018010321312968XI4Jex0kbvHal5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180103213129oQiGj1XcawYZmAP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}